29/04/2010
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- The New Kosovo Alliance party announced on Wednesday (April 28th) that the Republic of Vanuatu -- in the South Pacific, east of Australia -- has recognised Kosovo's independence. 
The foreign ministry has not commented on the announcement. 
(Lajm, Koha Ditore - 29/04/10; Telegrafi, Kohavision - 28/04/10)
